name: 杰米·麦克
introduction: Jaymee Mak is a Vancouver-based actor, filmmaker and marathon runner.In 2020, she released "It's Not You, It's Not Me.", a groundbreaking film about an asexual man (Lee Shorten from Man in the High Castle & AMC's The Terror) and sexual woman (Jaymee Mak from Supergirl), and their struggle to reconcile their different needs with their love for each other.In 2019, she won Best Film and Best Actress at Vancouver's Run N' Gun: Vancouver's 48-hour filmmaking competition, with her dramatic revenge film, "DeLISHH."Jaymee is a Senior Producer at Brace Yourself Games, an independent game studio best known as the creators of Crypt of the NecroDancer.
